==English==
=== Etymology ===
From the Latin ''[[disparatus]]'', the past participle of ''[[disparare]]'' "to divide" from ''[[dis-]]'' "apart" + ''[[parare]]'' "prepare"

=== Noun ===
'''disparateness'''
# the degree to which a thing is [[disparate]]
#: ''the '''disparateness''' of our group was truly our strength''

